common_questions.what_is_natal_type: Your natal type is your psychological blueprint - the core pattern of how you process information, make decisions, and interact with the world. It's determined by your birth date and reveals your authentic nature.
common_questions.how_accurate: The Deepsyke system is based on decades of research into human psychology and behavioral patterns. Thousands of people have found profound accuracy in their type descriptions.
common_questions.will_this_help: If you're seeking deeper self-understanding, clarity about your path, or insights into your patterns and behaviors, this approach provides a powerful framework for growth.
common_questions.time_commitment: Each conversation builds on the last. You can explore at your own pace - some prefer deep weekly sessions, others check in as questions arise.
common_questions.cost: This initial exploration is complimentary. We believe everyone deserves access to self-knowledge.

sample_feedback: Finally understanding my type explained so much about my life patterns.
The cultural avatars gave me permission to be authentically myself.
I've done years of therapy, but this framework tied everything together.
Knowing my type helped me make a major life decision with confidence.
The insights were eerily accurate and deeply validating.
